	quest.2D17D897B0458310.quest_desc: [
		"The Copper Machine is the foundation for the Steam Age. "
		""
		"What it does: This is the base block for all fluid-related machinery. You will need these to craft Spouts, Hose Pulleys, and many other fluid related Create components."
		""
		"While you can start by crafting these manually, they can be produced much more efficiently using Sequenced Assembly. Setting up a line of Deployers will save you resources and time as you scale up your factory!"
	]
