	quest.307FC9C96D669521.quest_desc: [
		"Andesite Alloy is the \"Iron\" of the mechanical world. It is the most important material for early progression, as it allows you to create your first shafts, gears, and kinetic machines."
		""
		"&lPro Tip&r: You are going to need a lot of this. Do not be afraid to clear cut nearby Andesite patches or look for ways to automate crushing Cobblestone into Andesite later on. You can also find plenty of it by looting chests in most structures."
	]
	quest.307FC9C96D669521.quest_subtitle: "Engineers First Mistake"
