	quest.3C707449948AA86E.quest_subtitle: "Can Duplcate Enchants?!?"
	quest.3E26ADD137287C32.quest_desc: [
		"In this pack, mastering the arts of Ars Nouveau is tied directly to your mechanical and magical progression. Instead of crafting individual glyphs, you unlock them in bulk by crafting specialized Codex Entries."
		""
		"&l&dHOW IT WORKS&r&r"
		""
		"Each tier of magic has a corresponding Codex Entry (Tier 1, Tier 2, etc.). Crafting these items will automatically grant you the knowledge for the glyphs within that level."
		""
		"&lTiered Unlocks&r: Craft the Codex Entry for a specific tier to instantly learn all the glyphs associated with it."
		""
		"&lDuplicate Protection&r: If you have already unlocked every glyph in a tier, crafting or using that tier’s entry again will grant you a significant burst of Experience instead!"
		""
		"&lStreamlined Magic&r: This system removes the \"hassle\" of individual glyph crafting, allowing you to focus on building your spells and automating your mana production."
	]
	quest.3E26ADD137287C32.quest_subtitle: "Spell Laziness Achieved"
	quest.3E2F6E71E5C4A4A2.quest_subtitle: "Up Up \\& U......p"
	quest.3F9BC53F02E12535.quest_desc: [
		"You shouldn't have to manually craft every single Essence for the rest of time. Once you have successfully crafted your first Essence of a specific type, you unlock the ability to reproduce that magic using your existing resources."
		""
		"The MAGIC loop!"
	]
