	quest.666794B19ADA2C73.quest_desc: [
		"The Fluid Sourcelink is a powerful generator that \"consumes\" various liquids to produce Source."
		""
		"&lHow to use&r: Simply pipe fluids into the link or place it next to a tank."
		""
		"The Source Condenser works in the opposite direction. It takes raw Source energy and \"condenses\" it into a liquid form. This can then be piped into tanks and or used to move source with pipes, trains, and such!"
	]
	quest.666794B19ADA2C73.quest_subtitle: "Magic Plumbing 101"
	quest.668629B241BF98A0.quest_subtitle: "FIND THAT BIOME!"
	quest.66D53C48AA60DA70.quest_desc: [
		"The Precision Mechanism represents the pinnacle of early-game engineering. These intricate components act as the \"high-tech\" brains of your factory, unlocking advanced logic, high-speed machinery, and the power of rotation control."
		""
		"&lStreamlined Assembly&r: Precision is in the name, but don't let that intimidate you! Thankfully, the recipe has been simplified to remove the chance of loss, making automation a lot simpler and more rewarding."
	]
	quest.66D53C48AA60DA70.quest_subtitle: "Masterpiece In Motion"
	quest.6750D7C8F88E6EC4.quest_subtitle: "Look Up to Grow \\& Down to Shrink"
